@startuml uc-3_class_relationships
!include ../../_theme.iuml

title UC-3 — View class relationships

|Student|
start
:Select an object in the tree;
|System|
:Use prebuilt `ClassGraph`
(created at app startup via `ClassGraphBuilder`);
:Compose relationship panel from graph edges
(Composes / Aggregates / References / Used By);
:Render UML tab via `AsciiUmlRenderer`;
|Student|
if (Click on a related class name?) then (yes)
    :Invoke `app.zoom_class(name)`;
    |System|
    :Re-render UML tab focused on the target class;
    |Student|
endif
stop

@enduml
